Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小焰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么  你就是传闻中变化无常的家伙么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会用奇怪的招数
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧  只是昏过去了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人  到底是谁的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是冷静的人的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无故挑起事端的笨蛋的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪种呢  佐仓杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在哪里见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全看不透你的牌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我就先撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明智呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要让我忠告多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟愚蠢到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不应该扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经说过很多次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对笨蛋我是不择手段的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小焰  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样  她有什么企图是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓美焰  你难道是…
